{"id":16382,"date":"2024-02-19T17:30:48","date_gmt":"2020-11-19T12:00:48","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=16382"},"modified":"2022-07-01T13:19:25","modified_gmt":"2022-07-01T07:49:25","slug":"contemporary-bathroom-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/contemporary-bathroom-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Contemporary Bathroom Design Ideas To Rejuvenate Your Senses"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Bathroom designs suited for your contemporary sensibilities<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Planning to overhaul your bathroom or just cannot wait to create a brand new one for your latest abode? It is just the right time to get inspired then! As most of you, homeowners will agree your bathroom is your sanctuary where you truly unwind, refresh and plan to win the world. It goes without saying that your contemporary bathroom speaks volumes about your home and your sensibilities. It ought to stand out. Although it might occupy a small space overall, yet it reveals the broader design of your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>By selecting luxe fittings, backdrops, paint, lights, you can transform a simple personal space into an enchanting contemporary bathroom that you would never want to leave.&nbsp; These curated ideas for contemporary bathroom designs will grow on your sensibilities in a blink on an eye. Have a look at all our picks right away:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tropical Contemporary Bathroom Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Who doesn\u2019t like to come back to a pacifying bathroom every day? Swept with blues and cool whites, the luxe fittings and indoor planters, make this <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bathroom-design\/\">bathroom design<\/a> too good to be missed. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165654\/tropical-contemporary-bathroom-design.jpg\" alt=\"Blue and cool white tropical contemporary bathroom designed with the luxe fittings and indoor planters looks soothing.\" class=\"wp-image-16393\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165654\/tropical-contemporary-bathroom-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165654\/tropical-contemporary-bathroom-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165654\/tropical-contemporary-bathroom-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165654\/tropical-contemporary-bathroom-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>This tropical bathroom design is cool and soothing<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bohemian Contemporary Bathroom Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Glass, indoor planters and chic partitions add incredible glam to even a simple bathroom. Go for minimalistic shower cabinets and place a plethora of planters around to create your natural bath in a jiffy. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165630\/bohemian-contemporary-bathroom-interiors.jpg\" alt=\"Glass enclosure shower and a plethora of planters around creates a natural bath with bohemian contemporary bathroom interiors.\" class=\"wp-image-16389\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165630\/bohemian-contemporary-bathroom-interiors.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165630\/bohemian-contemporary-bathroom-interiors-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165630\/bohemian-contemporary-bathroom-interiors-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165630\/bohemian-contemporary-bathroom-interiors-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Walk with the times and go for a subtly Bohemian style bathroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, more about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/bohemian-interior-design-and-decor\/\">Bohemian Interior Design And Decor<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black And White Contemporary Bathroom Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Simple, sophisticated and uber versatile, a black and white bathroom never goes out of style. Pick for your studio flat or a spacious abode, its consistent design calms your down any day. You can select black and white tiles or relevant wallpapers to make it outstanding.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165624\/black-_-white-contemporary-bathroom-tiles-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Contemporary bathroom tiles designs in black and white, partitioned with glass makes it outstanding.\" class=\"wp-image-16388\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165624\/black-_-white-contemporary-bathroom-tiles-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165624\/black-_-white-contemporary-bathroom-tiles-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165624\/black-_-white-contemporary-bathroom-tiles-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165624\/black-_-white-contemporary-bathroom-tiles-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Keep it classic and contemporary go for a black and white bathroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, read more about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/black-and-white-bathroom-design-ideas\/\">Black And White Bathroom Design Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wooden Contemporary Bathroom Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The texture of wood never fails to set a mark. Make use of wooden flooring and knick-knacks to grant a warm look to your bathroom. This design works well for every size of bathroom and strikes a great balance Indian and Western sensibilities.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165700\/wooden-contemporary-master-bathroom.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden flooring best contemporary bathroom with bathtub and plants around it grant a warm look to the bathroom.\" class=\"wp-image-16394\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165700\/wooden-contemporary-master-bathroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165700\/wooden-contemporary-master-bathroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165700\/wooden-contemporary-master-bathroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165700\/wooden-contemporary-master-bathroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Quintessentially contemporary, the vibe of this wooden bathroom is magical<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Minimalistic Contemporary Bathroom Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The future is going to be all about minimalistic design. Stay ahead of the curve and follow its suit for your bathroom as well. This bathroom design has Zen written all over it and it calms you down after a rough day. Align chiselled wooden panels, sleek mirror and turn it into a matchless bathroom then?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165648\/minimalistic-best-contemporary-bathroom-design.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalistic white contemporary master bathroom with a sleek mirror below wooden cabinet and zen bathtub looks seamless.\" class=\"wp-image-16392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165648\/minimalistic-best-contemporary-bathroom-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165648\/minimalistic-best-contemporary-bathroom-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165648\/minimalistic-best-contemporary-bathroom-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165648\/minimalistic-best-contemporary-bathroom-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Seamless, subtle and sight for eyes, a minimal bathroom pacifies everyone<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cosy Contemporary Bathroom Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There is something about cosy bathrooms that soothes you to the core. Go for grey tiles, luxe fittings and chic mirrors to light up a modest bathroom in no time. With glass panels, you could effortlessly divide and create a streamlined contemporary bathroom out of a modest layout. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165642\/cosy-contemporary-bathroom-tiles-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Glass partitioned modern contemporary bathroom design with grey tiles, luxe fittings and chic mirrors.\" class=\"wp-image-16391\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165642\/cosy-contemporary-bathroom-tiles-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165642\/cosy-contemporary-bathroom-tiles-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165642\/cosy-contemporary-bathroom-tiles-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165642\/cosy-contemporary-bathroom-tiles-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Call it your own, after all, who doesn\u2019t like an elegant, cosy bathroom?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Artistic Contemporary Bathroom Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Art is the essence of life. Let your bathroom stay true to it as well. Include metal knick-knacks, throw in a few planters over a broadly white palette made of tiles, bathtub, basins et al. See how it all beautifully unravels to create a magical bathroom. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165618\/artistic-modern-contemporary-bathroom-design.jpg\" alt=\"White tiles contemporary bathroom basins above metal knick-knacks and bathtub looks artistic bathroom.\" class=\"wp-image-16387\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165618\/artistic-modern-contemporary-bathroom-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165618\/artistic-modern-contemporary-bathroom-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165618\/artistic-modern-contemporary-bathroom-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/19165618\/artistic-modern-contemporary-bathroom-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Turn slightly eccentric, go for an artsy, contemporary bathroom!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All set to get a contemporary bathroom designed for your home? Well, we are sure our recommendations must have worked their magic. Feel free to reach us out if you need any assistance for creating your dream bathroom!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also Read:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/master-bathroom-ideas\/\">Master Bathroom Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/modern-bathroom-design-ideas\/\">Modern Bathroom Design Ideas<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Luxurious Modular Interior Design Ideas<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Design your personal oasis of comfort<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n          